    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently maintained by its previous owner. The engine starts reliably and runs smoothly, while the transmission provides a steady, comfortable driving experience. The interior is well-kept with only minor signs of wear on the seats and dashboard. On the exterior, there are a few light surface scratches consistent with normal use, but nothing that affects the car's overall solid appearance. It\u2019s a dependable vehicle ready for its next owner.",
